  "description": "A wide-angle landscape photograph depicts a waterfront scene with a focus on industrial buildings and distant, snow-capped mountains. The foreground features a constructed barrier of pale, vertical concrete or metal posts along the water's edge. Beyond this barrier lies a marshy area filled with dry, golden-brown vegetation. Several industrial buildings, including large rectangular structures with gray and white facades, are visible in the midground. In the far background, a mountain range dominates the horizon, its peaks covered with snow. The sky is a clear blue with scattered white clouds, providing a bright and airy backdrop. A crane is visible in the distance, highlighting the industrial nature of the area. The water in the foreground is a deep blue, reflecting the sky and creating a sense of depth.",
